(416, '\n				Patterson hopes Raptors can keep winning\n				', 'http://www.nba.com/2014/news/07/14/raptors-patterson.ap/index.html?rss=true\n			', ' Patrick Patterson saw the Raptors bring back guards Kyle Lowry and Greivis Vasquez and coach Dwane Casey, and he wanted to stay along for the ride.', 3, 1405379212, 'Mon, 14 Jul 2014 19:06:52 EDT', 0),
